flowchart TD
    A[Start Account Recovery] --> B{Is the user verified?}
    B -- Yes --> C[Proceed to Account Recovery]
    B -- No --> D[Send Verification Code]
    D --> E{Code Entered Correctly?}
    E -- Yes --> C
    E -- No --> F[Resend Verification Code]
    F --> E

    C --> G{Is the user requesting a number change?}
    G -- Yes --> H[Verify New Phone Number]
    H --> I{Is the new number verified?}
    I -- Yes --> J[Update Account with New Number]
    I -- No --> K[Notify User of Verification Failure]
    K --> H

    G -- No --> L[Handle Device Loss]
    L --> M[Verify Identity]
    M --> N{Identity Verified?}
    N -- Yes --> O[Secure Account Access]
    N -- No --> P[Notify User of Verification Failure]

    J --> Q[End Process]
    O --> Q